org.apache.flink.api.common.typeutils

Class CompositeType<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.api.common.typeinfo.TypeInformation<T>
      • org.apache.flink.api.common.typeutils.CompositeType<T>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    PojoTypeInfo, TupleTypeInfoBase

    public abstract class CompositeType<T>
extends TypeInformation<T>
    Type Information for Tuple and Pojo types The class is taking care of serialization and comparators for Tuples as well. See @see Keys class for fields setup.
